@startuml hyeonsangjeon_AWS-LLM-SageMaker

actor User
participant "Streamlit UI" as UI
participant "RAG System" as RAG
participant "SageMaker Endpoint\n(Korean LLM)" as LLM
participant "Amazon OpenSearch" as OpenSearch
participant "Embedding Model" as Embedding

User -> UI: Ask question
activate UI

UI -> RAG: Process query
activate RAG

RAG -> Embedding: Generate query embedding
activate Embedding
Embedding --> RAG: Query embedding
deactivate Embedding

RAG -> OpenSearch: Retrieve relevant documents
activate OpenSearch
OpenSearch --> RAG: Relevant documents
deactivate OpenSearch

RAG -> RAG: Construct prompt with retrieved info

RAG -> LLM: Send constructed prompt
activate LLM
LLM --> RAG: Generated response
deactivate LLM

RAG --> UI: Return answer
deactivate RAG

UI --> User: Display answer
deactivate UI

@enduml